Package: libtiff-bin-opengl
Version: 3.8.2
Revision: 1003
BuildDepends: libjpeg (>= 6b-3), fink (>= 0.9.9), glut
Depends: libjpeg-shlibs (>= 1.1.3-6), libtiff-shlibs (>= 3.8.2-1002)
Conflicts: libtiff-bin-nox
Replaces: libtiff (<< 3.5.7-5), libtiff-bin (<= 3.8.2-1002), libtiff-bin-nox
Source: ftp://ftp.remotesensing.org/libtiff/tiff-%v.tar.gz
Source-MD5: fbb6f446ea4ed18955e2714934e5b698
Patch: libtiff.patch
NoSetMAKEFLAGS: true
SetMAKEFLAGS: -j1
ConfigureParams: --mandir='${prefix}/share/man' --disable-dependency-tracking --without-apple-opengl-framework
GCC: 4.0
InstallScript: <<
 mkdir -p %i/share/man
 (export DESTDIR=%d; make install)
 rm -R %i/lib
 rm -R %i/include
 rm -R %i/share/man/man3
 rm -R %i/share/doc
<<
DocFiles: COPYRIGHT README
Description: Executables for libtiff package, with OpenGL support
DescPort: <<
DESTDIR support has been added upstream, so the previous gyrations 
to get this to install are no longer necessary.

A previous version compiled with -O3 at the suggestion of Blair Zajac,
but the trick for enabling this no longer works with the new build system.

Had to patch libtiff/Makefile.in to work around a problem with a missing
symbol in the new build system.

The --without-apple-opengl-framework and ax_cv_check_gl_libgl=no were added
to ensure that libtiff does not accidentally link against OpenGL.

Previous versions by Christoph Pfisterer.
<<
